      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Solid, honest driver with lots of character and a great way into the hobby. This car is in fair overall condition, showing its age with visible cosmetic wear and the kind of imperfections you\u2019d expect from a well-used classic, but it still presents as an enjoyable car you can drive and improve over time. A smart choice for someone who wants a usable enthusiast car without paying top-tier money.",
