      "description": "$46,700 - Mint-condition vehicle that shows exceptionally well inside and out. The exterior has a clean, glossy finish with little to no noticeable cosmetic wear, and the interior appears very well kept with minimal signs of use. This should be an excellent fit for a buyer looking for a standout, like-new example that needs no excuses.",
