    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle is a practical choice for a handy buyer, project seeker, or anyone needing affordable basic transportation. It shows clear wear consistent with age and use, but offers solid value at this price point and a chance to own for far less than newer alternatives. A straightforward opportunity for someone who sees potential and wants an inexpensive vehicle without overpaying.",
      "price": 3995.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car is a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport, a project to tinker with, or a handy runaround. It\u2019s not a showpiece, but it has honest character and offers a lot of value for the money. If you want something inexpensive and practical without spending a fortune, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with strong project potential. This car presents as a usable platform for someone who appreciates solid mechanical fundamentals and isn\u2019t afraid of a little cosmetic and deferred-maintenance sorting. The powertrain pulls through the rev range, the chassis feels planted, and it has the kind of straightforward, serviceable layout that makes it appealing as a budget commuter, shop car, or weekend fixer-upper. Not a showpiece, but a compelling buy for someone who wants affordable transportation with character and a good foundation to improve over time.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Sold as-is, priced to move fast. First serious buyer gets it.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with stories in its steel and plenty of road still left for the right next chapter. It has the kind of seasoned character you can\u2019t fake\u2014an honest, hard-used machine that stands out as a budget-friendly runabout, a hands-on project, or a practical spare to keep in the driveway. If you appreciate vehicles with grit, charm, and room to make it your own, this one offers a chance to get behind the wheel without a big upfront spend. A straightforward, no-pretense car with real potential for someone who sees value beyond the surface.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
